Documentation: The unique identifier of the LA account entry.
Is the unique identification of a client.
Unique identification of a partner object.
The process of creation holds the information during which use case the entry was created (e.g. LA registration, LA exchange, ...)
The LA ticket connected to the LA account entry is either the LA ticket which was created during the LA exchange or the LA ticket which was redeemed.
In case the LA account entry was created during some IG use cases (LA exchange, LA registration) the IG reference is stored.
In case the LA account entry was created during some OG use cases (LA exchange, LA registration) the OG reference is stored.
Additional information relevant for the LA account entry.
